===============================
=  README for ex2: Calculate  =
===============================

usage:	python3 ex2a.py 
		python3 ex2b.py


==================
=  Description:  =
==================
Second exercise.
First program will print different areas and peremiters according
to the shape chosen.
Second program functions as a basic calculator


=============================
=  List of submitted files: =
=============================

README			This file
ex2a.py    	    Contains the program to recieve a chosen shape from the user
                and prints it's area and peremiter according to the inputs
                specified (sides or radius)
ex2b.py     	Contains a program that functions as a calculator.
				It recieves 2 numbers (int) and an operation and prints
				the result of said operation.

